    "The study suggests that extending the training period and providing targeted professional development programs can significantly improve the interdisciplinary competencies of STEAM teachers.",
    "The proposed spiral curriculum model allows for continuous development and integration of knowledge and skills, ensuring that teachers are better equipped to handle the demands of STEAM education.",
    "The study also emphasizes the need for government support in terms of policy, preferential treatment, and professional title evaluation to encourage the growth of a qualified STEAM teaching workforce.",
